{"tid":2159331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"央視點名批評吃播浪費  吃播影片下架、直播主帳號即被封","createTime":"2020-08-16T09:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T09:14:15.000Z","uid":339805,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"edd8a1a545adc19cf730391f70bb1594ad6b9869","tid":2159331,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"近年中國大陸直播風氣興起，各個直播主都各施奇招吸引觀眾眼球，而當中就有一次進食大量食物的吃播出現。央視於 8 月 12 日點名批評「大胃王」、「吃播」等會誤導民眾浪費糧食。而不足 24 小時，網民發現被央視點名的帳號全數消失，從抖音或快手搜尋「大胃王」、「吃播」等字，更會彈出「文明吃播，珍惜糧食」等字樣。<br />\n<br />\n中國官媒央視於 8 月 12 日批評大陸近年流行的「大胃王」及「吃播」風氣是不文明的行為，嚴重誤導民眾浪費糧食，甚至公開點名批評部份「大胃王」直播主。而不足 24 小時，被央視公開點名批評的直播主帳號從社交媒體上全數消失。<br />\n <br />\n今日有網民嘗試在抖音或快手搜尋「大胃王」或「吃播」等字眼，更會彈出「文明吃播，珍惜糧食」等提示字樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/693f-ixreehp1912152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F693f-ixreehp1912152.jpg&h=94103cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而許多過去人氣頗高的吃播直播主影片被下架。部份直播主回應指，影片下架是為了作出轉型，亦有部份坦言是避免爭議而先行調整。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一張截圖顯示，有社交平台禁止大胃王吃播等主題，並指違規者將會被封號並不予解封。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/7017-ixreehp1911685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F7017-ixreehp1911685.jpg&h=3cc9b30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n部份大陸網民同意央視說法，並指控部分大胃王直播主是以吃完後催吐的方式嘩眾取寵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/e3d3-ixreehp1911245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fe3d3-ixreehp1911245.jpg&h=2cf1fe66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/33a3-ixreehp1911405.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F33a3-ixreehp1911405.jpg&h=c576c5bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上有人認為，近日習近平以及央視都高調批評浪費食物，加上中國大陸去年底爆發疫症及最近遭遇嚴重水災，令人聯想到中國或正面臨糧食不足的危機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/16/china-eating-live-are-banned-from-china-social-media/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F16%2Fchina-eating-live-are-banned-from-china-social-media%2Flife-tech%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=47cfbe14\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/16/china-eating-live-are-banned-from-china-social-media/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"363f9e3547ea92e91fc00bef4a2f7817ba8b8140","tid":2159331,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:13:30.000Z","msg":"唔生仔最節省啦下嘛<br />\n弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884aa39e068a084a3cd7882f32d18dc4b29c2bed","tid":2159331,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:14:15.000Z","msg":"吃肉不吃蒜，香味兒少一半"}]}